      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (compression-bending, 10 mm offset, 5 mm/min crosshead rate). Only one test condition was evaluated; the required level of 3 is not fully achieved because alternative loading rates or offset distances were not explored. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of the ASTM protocol."
